# Privacy and security

- Process meeting text locally; no backend or cloud AI in v1.
- Never log transcript, caption, or objective content in production.
- Never send meeting content over the network.
- Do not persist raw transcripts by default.
- New Chrome permissions require docs updates with justification.
- No remote scripts, analytics, or API keys.
